### Get All Users
GET http://localhost:8080/rede-segura/api/users
Accept: application/json

###

### Get User by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/rede-segura/api/users/2
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a New User
POST http://localhost:8080/rede-segura/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ana Pereira",
  "email": "ana.pereira@ufrn.br",
  "password": "senha123",
  "institutionId": 1,
  "rolesIds": [2]
}

###

### Update an Existing User
PUT http://localhost:8080/rede-segura/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ana Pereira Updated",
  "email": "ana.pereira@ufn.br",
  "password": "senha456",
  "institutionId": 1,
  "rolesIds": [1, 4]
}

###

### Delete a User
DELETE http://localhost:8080/rede-segura/api/users/1
Accept: application/json
